{"tid":633879,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"百萬富翁2018 又出錯題","createTime":"2018-04-18T16:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T11:17:02.000Z","uid":121784,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1baf13d1be9048290fa1c649727505736de8222","tid":633879,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"人類總要犯上相同的錯誤<br />\n繼之前&quot;邊個行星無衛星&quot;果題出錯之後,<br />\n今次又出錯科學題目<br />\n<br />\n18/4, 最後一名參賽者, 4000蚊果題.<br />\n<br />\n問題:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/003345_df45380b3ebd718438421e91b8175e2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F003345_df45380b3ebd718438421e91b8175e2a.jpg&h=917c6c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n答案應該為B 原子能, 而不是C 輻射能<br />\n<br />\n因為太陽是靠核聚變產生光和熱, 輻射只是用來傳播光和熱的途徑, 而非產生的途經.<br />\n<br />\n問題來啦~<br />\n上次出錯題, 參賽者放棄, 所以答中答錯都無分別<br />\n但今次參賽者用了50/50去除了B, 最後選擇了C而過關, 唔知今次亞視會點收科?"},{"pid":"b4e8705021263e0528b5784bbf9e25ca3e26419e","tid":633879,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"咁撚戇鳩？"},{"pid":"82bd46ddbc6f9d8c0a679fb7f5124ff17a26de06","tid":633879,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"係咪無腦<br />\n咁大個節目d人少少科學常識都無"},{"pid":"a8cc49dbcc761e6052ea050462e9d16bf4c2a182","tid":633879,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"出題前google下先都得啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca12cf4dcfd496b647b24a551c960c30dc6eebe9","tid":633879,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔柒唔係亞視"},{"pid":"d79d160346caa45c24ec842ae7fad677474b66d1","tid":633879,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"電視台出錯，參賽者又答錯